==English==
===Etymology===
From French ''[[échalote]]'', alteration of ''eschaloigne'', from Middle Latin ''escalonia'' "onion of [[w:Ascalon|Ascalon]]".

===Noun===
'''shallot'''

# a type of onion of the species [[Allium ascalonium]].
# a type of onion of the species [[Allium oschaninii]].
# any small onion.

